title: BIG TIME RIVALRY WEEK 2 MATCHUP
description:
Wendi Nix, Sam Acho, and EJ Manuel discuss a prime time rivalry matchup in Iowa and Iowa State. Sam and EJ breakdown the offensive and defensive keys to the game for both teams. Nicholls football head coach Tim Rebowe, also joins the show for an interview.
